WEBVTT

00:01.534 --> 00:03.985
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.955 --> 00:08.873
Hey, Sammy.

00:08.941 --> 00:10.391
Hey, Tim!

00:10.459 --> 00:12.059
I just heard the news.

00:12.127 --> 00:13.728
You had a fire?
Yeah.

00:13.796 --> 00:15.229
A couple weeks ago.

00:15.230 --> 00:16.329
Gee, the place looks great.

00:16.331 --> 00:17.381
Yeah, thanks a lot.

00:17.382 --> 00:18.683
We've been working pretty hard.

00:18.684 --> 00:20.619
We've got our grand reopening
tonight.

00:20.620 --> 00:22.169
So how'd the fire start?

00:22.237 --> 00:23.771
Oh, yeah, glad you asked.

00:23.839 --> 00:25.206
Sit down.
Right there.

00:25.274 --> 00:26.691
Right there, yeah.

00:26.809 --> 00:28.743
(chuckles)

00:28.811 --> 00:30.745
Rebecca!

00:30.813 --> 00:32.747
Right over there.

00:34.583 --> 00:36.351
I burned down the bar

00:36.419 --> 00:38.289
with a carelessly
tossed cigarette.

00:39.605 --> 00:41.373
It was a stupid thing to do

00:41.441 --> 00:44.242
and I will be paying for it
for the rest of my life.

00:50.599 --> 00:52.267
Hey, Sammy,

00:52.268 --> 00:53.634
you did a great job
on the rebuilding.

00:53.635 --> 00:55.036
The place looks
a million times better

00:55.037 --> 00:56.387
than it did before.
SAM: Yeah.

00:56.388 --> 00:57.706
Thanks, Paul.
Uh, Sammy,

00:57.773 --> 00:59.541
uh, Paul told me all
about the fire.

00:59.542 --> 01:00.709
Gee, that's tough, man.

01:00.710 --> 01:01.710
Oh, yeah, thank you.

01:01.711 --> 01:03.110
Oh, you want to hear
how it started?

01:03.111 --> 01:04.412
Yeah, sure.
Yeah! Great, great.

01:04.413 --> 01:06.298
Sit down right over there.

01:06.365 --> 01:08.300
Rebecca!

01:08.367 --> 01:10.477
Right over there
in the sweater- go ahead.

01:12.438 --> 01:15.640
I burned down the bar
with a carelessly tossed cigarette.

01:15.707 --> 01:17.224
It was a stupid thing to do

01:17.292 --> 01:19.927
and I will be paying for it
for the rest of my life.

